<!-- PJG ITAG l=84 g=1 f=1 -->
V. Significance of Risk
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
Before the Secretary can promulgate any permanent health or safety standard, he must find that a significant risk
of harm is present in the workplace and that the new standard is reasonably necessary to reduce or eliminate that risk.

