<!-- PJG ITAG l=11 g=1 f=1 -->
 and below. One comment noted that the interval after exposure at which the responses are evaluated can bias the results.
The comment added that the infrared energy or heat delivered to the skin during these exposures can affect and alter
the results. 
<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG 0012 frnewline -->

<!-- PJG /ITAG -->

<!-- PJG /STAG -->
